  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Tibial Insert Contact Stress Credibility Assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for a finite element model predicting tibial insert contact stress in a total knee arthroplasty (TKA) implant under physiological gait loading. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can predict peak contact stress and contact area at Model Risk Level 3 to support a 510(k) substantial equivalence claim for a Class II orthopaedic device. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels at MRL 3. Decision: Accepted.",
